# #
# # Usage: `foampeek [lib/app name query] [file name query]`
# #
# # Firstly, it prompts you to select a library (in `$FOAM_SRC`) or an application
# # (in `$FOAM_APP`), and finally, it lists all the files in that lib/app for you
# # to select.
